# Component Patterns

Structure: `src/components/[component-name]/`

- **`index.tsx`:** types at top, UI layout, `const` arrow function, default export
- **`hooks.ts`:** state and logic, returns `{ data, methods }`

```typescript
const Sidebar = () => {
  const { data, methods } = useHooks();
  // JSX only — no useState/useEffect here
};
export default Sidebar;
```

- `"use client"` on both files when using React client features
- UI atoms stay in `src/components/ui/` — import via `@/ui/*`
- Do not put page-specific logic in global components
